      • createPropertyGroupChangeSet

        public PropertyGroupChangeSet createPropertyGroupChangeSet(List<PropertyGroup> newPropertyGroups,
                                                           List<PropertyGroupChange> propertyGroupChanges,
                                                           List<String> removedPropertyGroupIds)
        Creates and returns a PropertyGroupChangeSet that can add, remove, and modify PropertyGroups on new or existing Cards.
        Parameters:
        newPropertyGroups - The PropertyGroups to be added to a Card (generated using a PropertyGroupFactory), or null to add none.
        propertyGroupChanges - PropertyGroupChanges for modifying existing PropertyGroups (generated using a PropertyGroupChangeFactory), or null to make no such changes.
        removedPropertyGroupIds - Strings containing the identifiers of PropertyGroups to be removed from a Card, or null to remove none.
        Returns:
        See above.
